data.name: CreateDashboardStagingPriority35
ReadDashboardStagingPriority1
data.value: select top(1) REPORT_MONTH, REPORT_LEVEL, REPORT_LEVEL_ID, AS_OF_DATE, CNTMPT_ORD_FILED from CKT_DB_STAGE_PRI35 where (REPORT_MONTH = @reportMonth) and (REPORT_LEVEL = @reportLevel) and (REPORT_LEVEL_ID = @reportLevelId)

data.name: ReadDashboardStagingPriority2
data.value: select REPORT_MONTH, REPORT_LEVEL, REPORT_LEVEL_ID, AS_OF_DATE, CNTMPT_ORD_FILED from CKT_DB_STAGE_PRI35 where (REPORT_MONTH = @reportMonth) and (REPORT_LEVEL in ('AT', 'CA'))

data.name: ReadFipsTribunal
data.value: select top(1) T1.[STATE], T1.COUNTY, T1.LOCATION, T1.COUNTY_DESC, T1.STATE_ABBREVIATION, T2.TRIBUNAL_NM, T2.JUDICIAL_DISTRICT, T2.IDENTIFIER from CKT_FIPS T1 join CKT_TRIBUNAL T2 on (T2.IDENTIFIER = @identifier) and (T1.LOCATION = T2.FIP_LOCATION) and (T1.COUNTY = T2.FIP_COUNTY) and (T1.[STATE] = T2.FIP_STATE) and (T1.COUNTY > 0)

data.name: ReadLegalAction
data.value: select LEGAL_ACTION_ID, CLASSIFICATION, ACTION_TAKEN, TYPE, FILED_DT, COURT_CASE_NO, END_DT, STANDARD_NO, CREATED_TSTAMP, ESTABLISHMENT_CD, TRB_ID from CKT_LEGAL_ACTION where (FILED_DT between cast(@date1 as date) and cast(@date2 as date)) and (CREATED_TSTAMP < @createdTstamp) and (CLASSIFICATION = 'O') and (ACTION_TAKEN = 'CONTEMPJ') order by CREATED_TSTAMP desc

data.name: ReadLegalActionAssigmentServiceProvider
data.value: select top(1) T1.LGA_IDENTIFIER, T1.OSP_EFFECTIVE_DATE, T1.OSP_ROLE_CODE, T1.OFF_GENERATED_ID, T1.SPD_GENERATED_ID, T1.EFFECTIVE_DT, T1.END_DT, T1.REASON_CODE, T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP, T2.SERVICE_PRVDER_ID, T2.USER_ID, T2.ROLE_CODE from CKT_SERVICE_PRVDER T2 join CKT_LA_SERV_PROV T1 on (@lgaIdentifier = T1.LGA_IDENTIFIER) and (T1.EFFECTIVE_DT <= cast(@createdTstamp as date)) and (T1.OSP_ROLE_CODE is not null) and (T1.OSP_EFFECTIVE_DATE is not null) and (T1.OFF_GENERATED_ID is not null) and (T2.SERVICE_PRVDER_ID = T1.SPD_GENERATED_ID) order by T1.EFFECTIVE_DT desc

data.name: UpdateDashboardStagingPriority1
data.value: update CKT_DB_STAGE_PRI35 set AS_OF_DATE = @asOfDate, CNTMPT_ORD_FILED = @cntmptOrdFiled where (REPORT_MONTH = @reportMonth) and (REPORT_LEVEL = @reportLevel) and (REPORT_LEVEL_ID = @reportLevelId)

data.name: UpdateDashboardStagingPriority2
data.value: update CKT_DB_STAGE_PRI35 set CNTMPT_ORD_FILED = @cntmptOrdFiled where (REPORT_MONTH = @reportMonth) and (REPORT_LEVEL = @reportLevel) and (REPORT_LEVEL_ID = @reportLevelId)
